show.description: Vikram married Ananya for her wealth, not love. With his lover Rhea, he plotted a perfect crime — a fake marriage that ended in cold-blooded murder. But when Ananya’s twin sister Avni steps in to claim the inheritance and uncover the truth, the hunter becomes the hunted. As secrets unravel and vengeance burns, only one will emerge victorious — the deceiver or the avenger.
